{"tid":597344,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"坤 哥 同 無 線 小 花 Helen 撐 枱 腳 斷 正","createTime":"2018-03-18T14:20:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-18T15:15:01.000Z","uid":35964,"like":30,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"b8abb080d637783b386fe31755b013ab4ef68148","tid":597344,"uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T14:20:39.000Z","msg":"睇真啲！再睇真啲！係！ 吳業坤同馬海倫撐枱腳！ 不過坤哥話：「 唔好傳緋聞。」 <br />\n<br />\n原來坤哥跟Helen Ma啱啱去完拜佛，兩個人於是就去大排檔食晏撐枱腳。Helen話跟坤哥合作過三個電視劇，算係有緣，所以約埋一齊拜佛，希望之後合作順利兼有高收視。而去年是非纏身，坤哥今年就求得好簽，事業跟愛情都有好轉。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uptow/i4/1cab0938c863aa5656db7526ebc1b114.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuptow%2Fi4%2F1cab0938c863aa5656db7526ebc1b114.png&h=74d8ebb0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"612b5897d197ad6961902a0d91ca52aaace990ea","tid":597344,"uid":172915,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T14:21:50.000Z","msg":"on9"},{"pid":"482677d2edb4de5020d5e8a50d0efab432281fa9","tid":597344,"uid":52571,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T14:29:41.000Z","msg":"坤哥我偶像<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52dcfc877577f83da84561a233b26c69a0eb9fc9","tid":597344,"uid":26573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T14:56:02.000Z","msg":"70路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d06e13bbe7e4a30b6a83c9096702d03243c209d9","tid":597344,"uid":78349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T14:56:39.000Z","msg":"屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"642aa617f6bdfb36739529febd5801465d76fb88","tid":597344,"uid":101110,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T14:58:12.000Z","msg":"咪撚po條偽毒垃圾上嚟宣傳啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15a1b4a1aa8fd607bf23a899f7c7c16cbd72b186","tid":597344,"uid":113956,"like":0,"d